data.title: ISRG vs. MDT: A High-Tech Robotics Faceoff in the Race for Leadership
data.description: Intuitive Surgical's robotics surge and Medtronic's broad innovation push set the stage for a high-tech showdown in next-gen minimally invasive care.
data.keywords: Intuitive Surgical, revenue growth, da Vinci, intelligent systems, installed base, Medtronic, digital ecosystems
